The warden of the [[Cannith enclave|Cannith Enclave (Dragon Towers)]] in [[Dragon Towers]], [[Sharn]], Dravot d'[[Cannith]] distinguished himself during his service with the elite [[Darkwood Watch]]. During the final decade of the [[Last War]], he served as the warden of the [[Whitehearth]] armory in [[Cyre]], but he was reassigned before the Day of [[Mourning]].